script:
1). Why don't you check with Ralph?
I didn't see him.
He doesn't want to.
I will. That's a good idea. 
2). When were the managers supposed to meet?
In the conference room.
To discuss procedures.
At 11 o'clock. 
3). Weren't you at the staff meeting?
Yes, you were.
No, I couldn't make it. 
He wasn't there.
